## 체크리스트

스토리 작성 완료 전 확인:

### MUST (Required)
- [ ] All content written in English?
- [ ] SectionTitle used for 2+ sections?
- [ ] Correct story type used? (autodocs for components, Doc for documentation)

### SHOULD (Recommended)
- [ ] PageContainer wrapping content (for Doc stories)?
- [ ] No Paper, Card, elevation decorations?
- [ ] Props documented in Table format?
- [ ] No excessive colors/decorations?
